sentences.english: He also created a functioning replica of MySpace's log-in page.
sentences.chinese: 斯克姆还创建了MySpace的登陆网页的复制品。

sentences.english: Enable logons to the data store server.
sentences.chinese: 启用登陆到数据存储服务器。
士兵离开运输航登陆了。

sentences.english: The landings called for an assault on a five-divisional front.
sentences.chinese: 登陆要求在五条分割的战线上进行突击。

sentences.english: The landing on moon heralds a new era of space.
sentences.chinese: 翻译月球登陆预示着航空史上又一个新时代的到来。

sentences.english: He landed with a guard of 500 men to sign the treaty.
sentences.chinese: 他偕同500人的警卫队一起登陆，签订条约。

sentences.english: As a matter of fact, extraterrestrials have landed.
sentences.chinese: 事实上，外星人登陆过地球。

sentences.english: How do I log on the company's intranet?
sentences.chinese: 我要如何登陆公司的办公网？

sentences.english: Hello, please login now to re-try the game.
sentences.chinese: 您好，请您现在重新登陆游戏。

sentences.english: They were coming in to land on the north coast of Crete .
sentences.chinese: 他们将从克里特岛北海岸登陆上岛。

sentences.english: Our mission is to harass the landing of the main japanese expeditionary force .
sentences.chinese: 我们的任务是骚乱日本远征军主力的登陆。

sentences.english: If aliens landed here right now, what would you do?
sentences.chinese: 如果此刻有外星人在此登陆，你会怎么做？

sentences.english: The beach defences were softened up before the landing craft was in.
sentences.chinese: 在登陆艇驶入以前，海滩防御工事已遭削弱。

sentences.english: While the link-sharing part of the service doesn't require a login, the bookmarking function does require users to register accounts.
sentences.chinese: 网址分享服务无需登陆，而书签功能则需要注册。

sentences.english: New sound when logging into pvp. net.
sentences.chinese: 新的登陆账号时开门声音。

sentences.english: When fascism comes to America, it will come wrapped in an America flag.
sentences.chinese: ‘法西斯主义登陆美国时，总会包着一面美国旗。’
